headline: Is Synchrony Financial (SYF) Still Attractive After Recent Share Price Pullback?
summary: If you are wondering whether Synchrony Financial at around US$72 a share still offers value, you are not alone. This article is built to help you make sense of the current price. headline: Synchrony and Planet DDS Expand Strategic Partnership to Integrate CareCredit Across Leading Dental Practice Management Platforms
summary: Synchrony (NYSE: SYF), a leading consumer financial services company, today announced an expanded strategic partnership with Planet DDS that helps orthodontic and dental practices simplify patient financing and makes it easier for patients to move forward with care.
